---
title: Cal Smart Maple-Glazed Bacon Salad with Roasted Veggies and Maple-Mustard Dressing
description: "Rendered bacon fat adds so much flavour to salad dressing, while sweet, smoky, crispy bacon pieces complement all the hearty roasted veggies in this super salad!

